Name: QA 8_Below Ground Pipework Checklist - Sewer - NMH
Set out pits depths and trench runs.
Pipes and fittings comply with relevant Authority and Specification.
Bedding placement and compaction and material meets specification.
Laying and jointing of pipes R.Ls and falls
Connections to pits and existing services
Hydrostatic tests are carried out as required.
Inspected and recorded by Independent Certifier or PIC (See attached)
Mirror tests are completed if required.
Placement and compaction of backfill and material meets spec.
Temporary cover provided to open drain.
PVC/ Plastic caps to open ends
As built information updated onto drawings
